[@Nertea](https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/83952-nertea/) I was able to get rid of one of my warnings for the B9 fuelSwitch duplicate entries by adding the following in CryoTanks\Patches\CryoTanksFuelTankSwitcher.cfg

Under the // ZBO tanks..

    !RESOURCE[LqdHydrogen] {}  

    // added the line below  

    !MODULE[ModuleB9PartSwitch]:HAS[#moduleID[fuelSwitch]] {}

    MODULE  

    {  

        name = ModuleB9PartSwitch  

        moduleID = fuelSwitch  

I figured that must be what was causing the warning, as the prior modification has the same thing.

Thanks for the great mods!
